  703          // жҸҸиҝ°: LINеөҢеҘ—еҗ‘йҮҸдёӯж–ӯжҺ§еҲ¶еҷЁеҲқе§ӢеҢ–.
  704          // еҸӮж•°: State:    дёӯж–ӯдҪҝиғҪзҠ¶жҖҒ, ENABLE/DISABLE.
  705          // еҸӮж•°: Priority: дёӯж–ӯдјҳе…Ҳзә§, Priority_0,Priority_1,Priority_2,Priority_3.
  706          // иҝ”еӣһ: жү§иЎҢз»“жһң SUCCESS/FAIL.
  707          // зүҲжң¬: V1.0, 2020-09-29
  708          //========================================================================
  709          u8 NVIC_LIN_Init(u8 State, u8 Priority)
  710          {
  711   1        if(State <= ENABLE) LIN_Interrupt(State); else  return FAIL;
  712   1        if(Priority <= Priority_3) LIN_Priority(Priority); else  return FAIL;
  713   1        return SUCCESS;
  714   1      }
